  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 97-19-57, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO INCREASE FROM $40.00 TO $100.00 THE SERVICE CHARGE FOR THE MAKING, DRAWING, ISSUING, UTTERING, DELIVERING, OR INITIATION OF A CHECK, DRAFT, ORDER, ELECTRONICALLY CONVERTED CHECK, OR ELECTRONIC COMMERCIAL DEBIT PAYMENT OF WHICH IS REFUSED BY THE DRAWEE DUE TO INSUFFICIENT FUNDS IN OR ON DEPOSIT WITH SUCH BANK, CORPORATION, FIRM OR PERSON; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
